WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 12]

01:49.950 --> 01:50.540
Qing Yi,

01:51.200 --> 01:52.540
you've had good catches these days.

01:53.480 --> 01:54.290
The weather's nice.

01:54.430 --> 01:55.930
The fish have come out to sun themselves.

02:05.510 --> 02:06.260
How come you haven't

02:06.430 --> 02:07.740
been looking for the Star Stone lately?

02:08.230 --> 02:09.460
Ten years, and still nothing.

02:10.150 --> 02:11.570
What's another day or two?

02:14.750 --> 02:15.730
What are you making?

02:16.680 --> 02:17.980
Your birthday present.

02:19.910 --> 02:21.340
How did you know it was my birthday?

02:22.470 --> 02:23.340
You're the clan chief.

02:24.150 --> 02:26.780
These past few days, all the women in the clan

02:27.520 --> 02:28.380
have been coming to ask me

02:28.430 --> 02:29.290
what you like.

02:30.560 --> 02:31.690
It would've been hard not to know.

02:32.750 --> 02:33.940
But this isn't really my birthday.

02:34.310 --> 02:35.010
I know

02:35.630 --> 02:37.170
it's not your actual birthday.

02:38.120 --> 02:39.060
That's why I never

02:39.520 --> 02:40.570
celebrated it before.

02:42.120 --> 02:43.690
Then why are you celebrating it this year?

02:47.150 --> 02:48.660
Maybe because we've been trapped here too long.

02:50.150 --> 02:51.220
As life goes on

02:53.030 --> 02:54.850
day by day in this illusion,

02:56.030 --> 02:57.660
everything's starting to feel

02:58.560 --> 02:59.940
half fake and half real.

03:01.680 --> 03:03.540
Besides, you've been taking care of me these past ten years.

03:03.800 --> 03:05.410
I want to do something to thank you too.

03:13.350 --> 03:14.100
What do you think?

03:20.200 --> 03:20.890
It looks great.

03:22.990 --> 03:24.020
They say

03:25.590 --> 03:26.960
bracelets made

03:26.960 --> 03:27.980
with langxi grass and shells

03:28.950 --> 03:30.860
are tokens of love between married flood dragons.

03:31.480 --> 03:33.020
They symbolize a love that lasts forever.

03:34.560 --> 03:36.180
Will you wear it every day from now on?

03:39.880 --> 03:40.480
I will.

03:46.280 --> 03:47.060
Mother!

03:49.030 --> 03:49.780
Mother...

03:49.870 --> 03:51.500
- Watch your step. - I found something special.

03:55.520 --> 03:56.780
Ten years have passed,

03:56.910 --> 03:58.340
yet you've barely grown.

03:59.710 --> 04:00.570
I don't know why either.

04:01.400 --> 04:02.850
When I was little, my parents always said

04:02.910 --> 04:03.940
I grew more slowly than other demons.

04:04.430 --> 04:05.060
Mother,

04:05.360 --> 04:08.610
this is my birthday gift for Father.

04:14.000 --> 04:14.450
Don't touch it.

04:25.160 --> 04:26.370
Didn't they say touching the Star Stone

04:27.040 --> 04:28.290
would free us from the illusion?

04:29.430 --> 04:31.220
This is only a fragment of it.

04:33.360 --> 04:34.050
Maybe

04:34.950 --> 04:36.370
only the complete Star Stone,

04:36.600 --> 04:37.460
activated with sacred power,

04:37.680 --> 04:38.490
will work.

04:40.160 --> 04:41.940
The Star Stone in Wu Zhiqi's hand

04:42.270 --> 04:43.870
did look as if it'd been mended.

04:44.750 --> 04:46.460
But why did the Star Stone shatter?

04:48.390 --> 04:50.370
Where are we supposed to find the rest of it?

04:55.390 --> 04:56.220
I remember now.

04:57.630 --> 04:58.410
When I was little,

04:59.050 --> 05:00.460
I used to play around here all the time.

05:01.310 --> 05:02.170
By accident,

05:02.720 --> 05:04.580
I dug up this strange little stone.

05:05.510 --> 05:07.610
Back then, I only thought it looked crystal-clear and pretty,

05:10.040 --> 05:11.460
so I took it home to my parents.

05:12.600 --> 05:14.340
Then how did this fragment

05:15.600 --> 05:17.220
end up in Wu Zhiqi's hands?

05:18.630 --> 05:20.290
Did you ever meet Wu Zhiqi?

05:22.870 --> 05:24.140
Actually, I've lost my memories

05:26.000 --> 05:27.460
of the day my clan was slaughtered.

05:29.040 --> 05:29.810
For some reason,

05:30.720 --> 05:31.730
I fainted that day.

05:36.090 --> 05:37.120
By the time I woke up,

05:37.600 --> 05:38.410
the others in my clan

05:38.410 --> 05:40.290
had already been slaughtered by the Shilin Sect.

05:42.070 --> 05:42.780
I think I saw

05:43.560 --> 05:45.170
Wu Zhiqi that day.

05:47.510 --> 05:48.810
No wonder every time I urged you

05:50.160 --> 05:51.280
to keep looking for the Star Stone,

05:51.280 --> 05:52.340
you always dodged it,

05:52.680 --> 05:54.340
using Shiguang or being busy

05:54.950 --> 05:55.850
as an excuse.

05:56.270 --> 05:57.050
In truth,

05:57.800 --> 05:58.850
you wanted to stay here

05:59.310 --> 06:00.610
until the slaughter

06:01.720 --> 06:03.250
to see what really happened,

06:04.310 --> 06:04.900
right?

06:09.120 --> 06:09.850
I'm sorry.

06:11.510 --> 06:13.140
Why are you apologizing all of a sudden?

06:13.950 --> 06:14.980
Because I kept stopping you.

06:16.870 --> 06:17.850
You wanted to leave.

06:19.560 --> 06:20.580
I shouldn't have stopped you.

06:23.270 --> 06:24.700
You wanted me to stay and keep you company,

06:26.510 --> 06:27.220
right?

06:33.870 --> 06:35.170
This illusion is fake,

06:36.270 --> 06:37.540
but the feelings are real.

06:38.600 --> 06:39.850
Are you sure you want to stay

06:40.630 --> 06:42.780
and go through something that cruel all over again?

06:46.270 --> 06:47.170
To me,

06:47.750 --> 06:48.660
not knowing the truth

06:50.240 --> 06:51.580
is the cruelest thing of all.

06:53.070 --> 06:54.100
Then I won't leave either.

06:55.190 --> 06:56.140
I'll stay here with you.

06:57.160 --> 06:58.100
Having someone beside you

06:58.750 --> 07:00.100
will at least make it a little easier.

07:04.270 --> 07:04.930
Thank you.

07:09.360 --> 07:10.050
This time,

07:10.750 --> 07:11.660
I must find out

07:11.680 --> 07:13.750
what really happened at the Blackwater River back then.

07:17.950 --> 07:18.660
Blackwater River?

07:23.310 --> 07:23.930
What is it?

07:26.800 --> 07:27.490
Di Zhu,

07:28.240 --> 07:30.080
I know you like pretty stones.

07:31.070 --> 07:33.180
This is the Radiant Moon.

07:33.240 --> 07:34.210
I plan

07:34.270 --> 07:35.480
to give it to you

07:35.480 --> 07:37.470
at the prayer ceremony before your wedding.

07:45.000 --> 07:45.730
Don't worry.

07:46.800 --> 07:47.850
I know

07:48.160 --> 07:49.220
Man Man isn't the killer.

07:49.630 --> 07:50.700
I won't have him burned to death.

07:54.390 --> 07:55.290
That won't do.

08:09.270 --> 08:10.100
Di... Di Zhu,

08:10.270 --> 08:11.400
what are you doing?

08:40.870 --> 08:41.770
I understand everything now.

08:42.670 --> 08:43.300
Too bad

08:44.270 --> 08:45.700
your plan is going to fail.

08:47.440 --> 08:49.130
You've lost all your sacred power.

08:49.840 --> 08:50.980
How are you going to stop me?

08:56.390 --> 08:58.010
Looks like the killer is hiding in the shadows.

08:58.200 --> 08:59.060
You're in great danger.

08:59.510 --> 09:01.260
I'll undo the sacred power seal on you

09:01.670 --> 09:02.720
just in case.

09:10.870 --> 09:11.420
Lu Wuyi.

09:38.240 --> 09:39.940
Chief Ao, do you know that Sun is a snake demon?

09:42.200 --> 09:43.530
He came for the Star Stone too.

09:43.960 --> 09:44.580
Fortunately,

09:44.790 --> 09:46.440
Di Zhu and I drove him off.

09:49.030 --> 09:50.730
Now all you have to do is put this hairpin

09:50.840 --> 09:51.770
in his room,

09:52.510 --> 09:53.420
and he'll be the killer.

10:14.600 --> 10:15.370
Water...

10:16.600 --> 10:17.300
Water...

10:20.030 --> 10:20.900
Water...

10:21.320 --> 10:22.150
Drop the act.

10:22.360 --> 10:23.340
Your father's already gone.

10:26.840 --> 10:27.890
Water.

10:33.550 --> 10:34.250
Water.

10:49.480 --> 10:50.300
Thank you, Man Man.

10:54.030 --> 10:55.260
Thank you, Ji Ling.

10:58.120 --> 11:00.060
It's not every day that I get to see Master Chi Wen's tender side.

11:00.490 --> 11:02.180
Of course I had to keep acting a little longer.

11:03.390 --> 11:04.250
After all, Master Chi Wen

11:05.240 --> 11:07.400
doesn't usually wipe my sweat

11:07.400 --> 11:08.480
with his sleeve.

11:09.270 --> 11:10.420
I can also give you a slap.

11:10.840 --> 11:11.820
It'll have about the same effect.

11:12.390 --> 11:13.180
Want to try it?

11:14.960 --> 11:15.610
What,

11:16.910 --> 11:18.220
are you trying to avenge Ji Ling?

11:21.120 --> 11:22.610
You were possessed by a demon.

11:23.390 --> 11:25.300
How are you still in the mood to talk nonsense?

11:25.870 --> 11:26.940
You've really got a strong heart.

11:30.080 --> 11:31.220
Master Chi Wen,

11:31.910 --> 11:33.490
didn't you say I had no heart?

11:34.510 --> 11:36.370
Why are you saying I have a strong heart now?

11:37.840 --> 11:40.980
What do you really think of me?

11:42.360 --> 11:42.890
You...

11:44.360 --> 11:45.370
Calm down.

11:46.150 --> 11:47.580
Once Ao Erlie gets back,

11:47.840 --> 11:48.770
I'll use Word Magic on him,

11:48.910 --> 11:50.220
and we'll know where the Star Stone is.

11:50.480 --> 11:51.490
Why bother catching the demon?

11:52.240 --> 11:53.700
If you don't want to be burned to death,

11:53.910 --> 11:54.770
you'd better run.

11:57.750 --> 11:59.770
The Shilin Sect has countless books.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.060
Haven't you read this saying?

12:02.360 --> 12:04.060
"Husband and wife are like birds from the same forest,

12:04.750 --> 12:06.010
but when disaster strikes..."

12:07.200 --> 12:07.980
They fly away together.

12:46.600 --> 12:47.940
No return.

12:54.720 --> 12:55.850
No finding it again.

13:05.510 --> 13:06.370
Let go, Master!

13:08.670 --> 13:09.700
Master Dragon Deity,

13:13.440 --> 13:14.650
I hope you are well.

13:29.270 --> 13:30.130
This demon mark...

13:31.600 --> 13:32.340
It was painted.

13:33.720 --> 13:34.980
I'm not a Green Ape.

13:35.790 --> 13:37.060
Yuan Wuhuo lied to me.

13:54.270 --> 13:54.890
What's wrong?

13:56.030 --> 13:56.980
Pouting again?

14:00.550 --> 14:01.340
After all these years,

14:02.870 --> 14:04.730
are you still blaming me for forcing you to swallow

14:05.320 --> 14:06.250
the Dragon Marrow?

14:09.960 --> 14:11.250
You actually forced your own brother...

14:12.870 --> 14:14.730
forced me to swallow the Dragon Marrow?

14:15.960 --> 14:17.180
You were blind from childhood,

14:18.150 --> 14:19.300
frail and sickly too.

14:21.120 --> 14:21.940
To grow stronger,

14:22.870 --> 14:24.060
of course you needed to take something strong.

14:24.600 --> 14:25.770
I can't possibly

14:25.770 --> 14:27.250
follow you around and protect you

14:27.510 --> 14:28.250
forever.

14:29.150 --> 14:30.420
Besides, when I'm not around,

14:31.440 --> 14:33.010
who's supposed to protect Father and Mother?

14:34.550 --> 14:35.820
When I'm not around,

14:36.550 --> 14:37.980
who's supposed to protect Father and Mother?

14:39.030 --> 14:39.890
Xizai,

14:40.600 --> 14:41.370
we need

14:41.870 --> 14:43.530
a protector in the family.

14:45.630 --> 14:46.220
Wuhuo!

14:46.390 --> 14:48.010
- Take it! - No!

14:48.010 --> 14:49.420
- Swallow it! - No!

14:49.440 --> 14:50.130
Swallow it!

14:54.080 --> 14:55.260
After you took the Dragon Marrow,

14:56.270 --> 14:57.460
you not only gained sacred power

14:58.120 --> 14:59.130
and got rid of your illness,

15:00.000 --> 15:01.130
but it also healed your eyes

15:01.630 --> 15:02.580
and gave you back your sight.

15:03.440 --> 15:04.850
You should be thanking me.

15:06.200 --> 15:07.460
You made choices for my life

15:09.080 --> 15:10.820
out of your own self-righteousness,

15:11.320 --> 15:13.010
and you expect me to thank you for it?

15:14.080 --> 15:14.890
You're right.

15:18.960 --> 15:20.130
But what's done is done.

15:20.750 --> 15:21.940
There's no point regretting it.

15:23.030 --> 15:23.940
Regret

15:24.270 --> 15:25.700
is the most pointless

15:26.080 --> 15:28.060
and yet the most tormenting feeling in the world.

15:29.550 --> 15:31.010
Look at this chaotic world.

15:32.150 --> 15:33.250
If you want to survive,

15:33.870 --> 15:34.580
you have to be ruthless.

15:35.600 --> 15:36.700
Ruthless to others,

15:37.840 --> 15:38.940
and even more ruthless to yourself.

15:39.790 --> 15:40.770
To be ruthless enough,

15:41.440 --> 15:42.610
you first have to learn

15:43.240 --> 15:44.010
how not to regret.

15:49.630 --> 15:51.220
What you need isn't regret.

15:54.390 --> 15:55.460
It's repentance.

16:06.320 --> 16:07.730
You made me swallow the Dragon Marrow,

16:08.120 --> 16:10.100
join the Shilin Sect, and become a demon hunter.

16:10.870 --> 16:12.280
So why are we disguising ourselves

16:12.280 --> 16:13.220
as Green Ape demons now?

16:17.030 --> 16:17.790
Because we have to

16:17.790 --> 16:18.990
steal the Star Stone before midnight

16:19.270 --> 16:20.100
tomorrow night.

16:20.670 --> 16:22.460
Once it's sent to the battlefield,

16:22.960 --> 16:24.060
there will hardly be another chance.

16:25.390 --> 16:26.220
The Star Stone?

16:30.840 --> 16:32.940
Father and Mother named us Xizai and Wuhuo

16:33.480 --> 16:35.220
in the hope that we'd live free of disaster and misfortune.

16:35.910 --> 16:37.940
The Star Stone has the power to destroy heaven and earth.

16:38.480 --> 16:39.130
With it,

16:40.000 --> 16:41.460
we can defeat the demon clans

16:42.670 --> 16:44.060
and end this war once and for all,

16:45.720 --> 16:48.010
making the world truly free of disaster and misfortune.

16:49.080 --> 16:49.940
A butterfly demon.

16:51.550 --> 16:52.940
He said his name was Yuan Wuhuo,

16:55.480 --> 16:57.100
Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing".

16:58.240 --> 16:59.250
Your name

17:00.630 --> 17:01.730
is Yuan Wuhuo?

17:04.030 --> 17:05.060
Huo as in "misfortune"?

17:09.440 --> 17:10.220
Having silly thoughts again?

17:14.640 --> 17:15.700
The cave where the Star Stone is hidden

17:15.880 --> 17:16.530
is nearby.

17:17.310 --> 17:17.810
Let's go.

17:18.310 --> 17:18.980
Put on your mask.

17:19.790 --> 17:20.860
We're going to find Wu Zhiqi.

17:25.110 --> 17:25.730
Something's off.

17:27.160 --> 17:28.570
No return.

17:29.110 --> 17:30.530
No return.

17:32.400 --> 17:33.700
No finding it again.

17:35.070 --> 17:35.940
Your name

17:37.550 --> 17:38.730
is Yuan Wuhuo?

17:40.680 --> 17:42.010
He's not Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "free of misfortune"]

17:43.110 --> 17:44.770
He's Yuan Wuhuo, the butterfly demon.
[*Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing"]

17:51.110 --> 17:51.730
Father,

17:52.110 --> 17:53.220
I don't want these marks anymore.

17:55.400 --> 17:56.090
What is it?

17:57.160 --> 17:58.660
Don't you like what I drew?

18:00.200 --> 18:01.810
Your mother's eyes haven't been good lately.

18:02.440 --> 18:03.530
Make do with these for now.

18:06.640 --> 18:08.530
You both have

18:08.790 --> 18:09.660
demon marks.

18:10.000 --> 18:12.090
How come I have to wear fake ones to fool people?

18:17.110 --> 18:17.900
They all say

18:18.200 --> 18:20.770
I don't have demon marks

18:21.200 --> 18:23.010
because I'm not really your child.

18:28.350 --> 18:28.770
Come here.

18:34.720 --> 18:35.380
Shiguang,

18:36.750 --> 18:37.700
listen to me.

18:43.400 --> 18:44.770
You are my child.

18:46.720 --> 18:47.800
You're the one

18:48.200 --> 18:48.940
your mother

18:49.720 --> 18:50.290
and I

18:51.030 --> 18:51.900
love most in this world.

18:52.550 --> 18:54.180
That will never change.

19:02.720 --> 19:04.180
You're the one your mother and I

19:05.000 --> 19:05.860
love most in this world.

19:07.240 --> 19:09.090
That will never change.

19:14.640 --> 19:15.250
Shiguang,

19:15.790 --> 19:16.620
from now on,

19:17.030 --> 19:17.980
if you don't want to wear demon marks,

19:18.440 --> 19:19.330
we won't paint them.

19:20.240 --> 19:20.730
No,

19:21.160 --> 19:22.010
I want them.

19:22.750 --> 19:23.620
Father said

19:24.200 --> 19:25.940
the demon marks are the symbol of the flood dragon clan.

19:26.480 --> 19:28.180
They stand for courage and strength.

19:28.200 --> 19:30.010
My demon marks are painted by Mother and Father.

19:30.550 --> 19:32.490
That means you two are my courage and strength.

19:51.240 --> 19:51.860
Well?

19:52.830 --> 19:53.530
Did you get it out of him?

19:54.110 --> 19:54.940
Where's the Star Stone?

19:56.000 --> 19:57.050
The Word Magic didn't work.

19:58.200 --> 19:59.050
My demon magic

19:59.590 --> 20:00.980
keeps failing me at the crucial moment.

20:02.310 --> 20:03.860
The power of the Formless Moon members

20:04.790 --> 20:05.860
is tied to the moon.

20:07.480 --> 20:08.180
Maybe

20:08.790 --> 20:10.010
it's daytime outside right now.

20:11.000 --> 20:11.900
With the moonlight hidden,

20:12.270 --> 20:13.660
it becomes harder for you to use magic.

20:15.960 --> 20:18.090
Now I believe you're really the Dragon Deity.

20:19.160 --> 20:20.380
That fool Ji Ling

20:20.590 --> 20:21.770
would never know so much.

20:26.110 --> 20:27.250
Aren't you a fox demon?

20:28.440 --> 20:29.050
Why

20:30.310 --> 20:32.290
does your compliment sound so unflattering?

20:33.680 --> 20:35.050
Ji Ling, that silly boy.

20:36.070 --> 20:37.940
All he'd do was hold out a handful of raspberries...

20:39.270 --> 20:40.420
I picked these out for you.

20:40.680 --> 20:41.330
They're all sweet.

20:42.000 --> 20:43.460
And insist I eat them

20:43.880 --> 20:44.900
because they were sweet.

20:51.160 --> 20:52.460
Since Word Magic doesn't work now,

20:53.200 --> 20:54.090
the only way left

20:54.110 --> 20:55.090
is to wait until the wedding day

20:55.400 --> 20:56.920
to get the Star Stone.

21:00.310 --> 21:01.330
Master Chi Wen,

21:02.310 --> 21:03.730
do you really want to marry me?

21:05.830 --> 21:07.620
It's Man Man who wants to marry Di Zhu.

21:10.110 --> 21:11.050
Then tell me,

21:12.680 --> 21:14.490
would Man Man be willing to kiss Di Zhu?

21:22.200 --> 21:23.810
I can find the Star Stone tonight.

21:24.310 --> 21:25.090
Want to make a bet?

21:25.310 --> 21:26.050
What's the wager?

21:27.200 --> 21:28.090
If I win,

21:28.590 --> 21:30.140
you'll give me my favorite thing.

21:31.640 --> 21:32.620
In this snow and ice,

21:32.920 --> 21:34.220
where am I supposed to pick flowers for you?

21:44.680 --> 21:45.330
I win.

21:50.070 --> 21:51.290
Only Ji Ling would know

21:53.070 --> 21:54.460
that flowers are my favorite,

21:56.200 --> 21:57.220
that I only like flowers.

22:06.550 --> 22:08.050
The day you left the Shilin Sect,

22:11.160 --> 22:12.700
Ji Ling insisted on seeing you off.

22:15.750 --> 22:16.660
I saw him

22:17.070 --> 22:19.010
picking flowers under the Golden Scale Tree,

22:21.440 --> 22:22.530
so I asked him why.

22:24.920 --> 22:25.730
He said

22:27.310 --> 22:28.220
you liked flowers

22:30.000 --> 22:31.460
and insisted on picking some for you.

22:43.510 --> 22:44.860
There are no flowers here,

22:47.030 --> 22:47.940
but I can...

22:47.960 --> 22:48.660
You can kiss me?

22:52.680 --> 22:54.460
I can make some for you myself.

23:03.550 --> 23:04.290
I have an idea!

23:08.160 --> 23:09.140
Why are you

23:09.160 --> 23:10.570
making such a fuss?

23:17.720 --> 23:18.570
You scared it.

23:27.960 --> 23:28.940
Everyone,

23:29.920 --> 23:30.940
the prayer ceremony

23:31.480 --> 23:33.250
has always been an Aodeng tradition.

23:33.880 --> 23:34.770
But now,

23:35.270 --> 23:36.250
the Radiant Moon

23:36.550 --> 23:37.810
has suddenly gone missing!

23:38.830 --> 23:40.260
- What? - What happened?

23:41.110 --> 23:42.570
Does this have to do with your plan?

23:44.200 --> 23:44.900
Genius, right?

23:45.920 --> 23:46.460
Chief Ao,

23:46.960 --> 23:48.460
such an ill omen

23:49.070 --> 23:50.420
shows that Di Zhu and Man Man

23:51.000 --> 23:52.050
are not a good match at all.

23:52.400 --> 23:52.940
I suggest

23:53.110 --> 23:54.980
their wedding be postponed.

24:02.000 --> 24:03.530
If two people love each other, they're a good match.

24:04.030 --> 24:05.420
How can you deny our love

24:05.590 --> 24:06.980
because of a single stone?

24:09.310 --> 24:10.980
Right, Man Man?

24:15.030 --> 24:16.250
Answer me.

24:17.480 --> 24:17.940
Right.

24:19.550 --> 24:19.980
Right.

24:22.130 --> 24:23.380
That's right.

24:23.550 --> 24:24.220
True.

24:24.400 --> 24:25.420
My love for Di Zhu

24:26.240 --> 24:28.010
is like this beautiful everlasting flower.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.180
It will never fade.

24:42.440 --> 24:43.090
Next time,

24:43.720 --> 24:45.490
I'll make you a flower

24:45.550 --> 24:46.050
that will never wither.

24:46.590 --> 24:47.180
All right?

24:50.440 --> 24:51.490
Take it.

24:54.550 --> 24:56.660
- Good! - Good!

24:57.000 --> 24:57.990
All right, enough.

24:58.310 --> 24:59.490
Everyone, listen.

25:00.000 --> 25:00.850
The prayer ceremony

25:00.850 --> 25:02.460
is only two days away.

25:02.880 --> 25:04.220
Now that the Radiant Moon is gone,

25:04.590 --> 25:05.640
where are we supposed to find

25:05.640 --> 25:07.330
another gem that fine?

25:09.070 --> 25:10.050
Use the Star Stone.

25:10.550 --> 25:12.220
It was meant to be my dowry anyway.

25:12.440 --> 25:13.940
Nothing is more precious

25:14.200 --> 25:15.380
or brings greater blessings than that.

25:16.960 --> 25:17.980
Di Zhu is right.

25:18.720 --> 25:20.490
I'll get the Star Stone now.

25:26.200 --> 25:26.810
So?

25:32.070 --> 25:32.660
Praise me.

25:33.960 --> 25:34.380
Impressive.

25:39.920 --> 25:40.700
So that means

25:41.510 --> 25:43.770
I'll have the Star Stone tonight.

25:47.880 --> 25:49.530
That demon is after the Star Stone.

25:50.200 --> 25:51.810
You and I should join forces first to capture it,

25:51.900 --> 25:52.940
then deal with the Star Stone.

26:05.440 --> 26:05.940
Chief Cang.

26:07.400 --> 26:07.860
Chief Cang,

26:08.110 --> 26:09.420
why do you wear the bracelet

26:09.480 --> 26:10.570
Qing Yi made for you every single day?

26:11.440 --> 26:13.250
A bracelet symbolizes lasting love.

26:13.880 --> 26:15.900
It should be put away properly.

26:16.160 --> 26:17.570
Don't wear it every day.

26:17.830 --> 26:18.860
If it broke,

26:19.070 --> 26:19.940
it'd invite bad luck.

26:20.400 --> 26:21.750
It must be Qing Yi's fault.

26:22.000 --> 26:23.620
I told her it should

26:23.750 --> 26:24.730
be put away

26:24.730 --> 26:25.700
and kept safe.

26:25.750 --> 26:26.770
That careless girl.

26:27.480 --> 26:28.900
She must've forgotten to tell you.

26:29.160 --> 26:29.980
They say

26:31.160 --> 26:32.420
bracelets made

26:32.440 --> 26:33.570
with langxi grass and shells

26:34.590 --> 26:36.530
are tokens of love between married flood dragons.

26:36.960 --> 26:38.140
They symbolize a love that lasts forever.

26:39.030 --> 26:40.620
Will you wear it every day from now on?

26:43.350 --> 26:44.250
She did tell me.

26:45.270 --> 26:46.330
I just liked it so much that I

26:47.070 --> 26:47.900
decided to wear it every day.

28:11.830 --> 28:12.730
Another nightmare?

28:22.920 --> 28:23.570
It's all right.

28:24.640 --> 28:25.420
It was just a dream.

28:29.310 --> 28:30.220
Go back to sleep.

28:32.480 --> 28:33.530
If anything comes up, call for me.

28:35.790 --> 28:36.420
Don't go.

28:41.350 --> 28:41.900
What,

28:43.200 --> 28:44.570
are you finally letting me sleep in the big bed?

28:47.200 --> 28:47.940
Don't go.

30:10.160 --> 30:10.770
Back then,

30:11.830 --> 30:12.700
I thought that since the Star Stone

30:12.720 --> 30:14.660
could cure the plague in Aodeng,

30:16.880 --> 30:18.420
it should also be able to cure

30:19.400 --> 30:20.980
my younger brother of his illness.

30:21.750 --> 30:24.180
So I sent Man Man to steal the Star Stone.

30:25.400 --> 30:26.420
But instead,

30:27.400 --> 30:29.250
it led to the destruction of the entire Aodeng clan.

30:30.240 --> 30:31.180
So the Star Stone didn't work?

30:35.350 --> 30:35.860
It didn't.

30:37.790 --> 30:38.420
Maybe

30:38.640 --> 30:40.530
that was heaven's punishment for me.

30:41.480 --> 30:43.700
Heaven took my little brother too.

30:45.750 --> 30:47.660
A mortal killed him.

30:50.960 --> 30:52.290
How dare you hurt me?

30:52.550 --> 30:54.140
I left the silver on your stall.

30:54.160 --> 30:54.900
I didn't steal anything!

30:55.350 --> 30:56.490
What silver?

30:56.720 --> 30:57.810
There was no silver at all!

30:58.070 --> 30:58.860
I really did give it to him!

30:58.960 --> 31:00.540
- He's a thief! - How dare you steal from me?

31:00.540 --> 31:01.460
How dare you?

31:01.680 --> 31:03.540
How dare you?

31:03.920 --> 31:05.730
All he wanted was to buy a clay figurine

31:07.070 --> 31:08.830
as a birthday gift for me.

31:10.440 --> 31:11.490
Who would've thought...?

31:13.310 --> 31:14.930
A mortal beating a young demon to death...

31:15.830 --> 31:17.250
Was that the Yuan Clay Incident that sparked the war

31:17.250 --> 31:18.190
between humans and demons?

31:20.480 --> 31:21.070
That's right.

31:22.440 --> 31:24.180
At the time, people didn't think much of it.

31:24.720 --> 31:26.180
But Yuan's death

31:27.270 --> 31:28.730
became the spark that lit

31:28.830 --> 31:30.140
the flames of anger and hatred.

31:31.400 --> 31:32.420
Conflicts between humans and demons

31:32.440 --> 31:33.700
broke out across the land,

31:34.310 --> 31:36.460
and in the end, it led to a century-long war.

31:39.110 --> 31:39.530
Chief Wu,

31:41.400 --> 31:42.660
may I take a look at this clay figurine?

31:59.240 --> 32:01.010
A figurine holding a longevity peach.

32:07.510 --> 32:09.180
Your brother really put thought into the gift

32:11.000 --> 32:11.860
he picked for you.

32:52.590 --> 32:53.010
Hey there.

32:54.510 --> 32:55.660
What a stupid thief.

32:56.640 --> 32:56.980
Stupid?

32:57.920 --> 32:59.940
Can't you tell my family's poor?

33:00.350 --> 33:01.940
Why did you come to steal from us?

33:02.200 --> 33:02.600
Look.

33:02.920 --> 33:04.220
This is the best robe we have

33:04.640 --> 33:05.290
in the house,

33:05.880 --> 33:07.460
yet it's been patched up hundreds of times.

33:07.920 --> 33:09.290
That robe of yours looks pretty new.

33:09.680 --> 33:11.180
Take it apart, and I could make two out of it.

33:12.030 --> 33:13.290
Little one,

33:13.790 --> 33:14.940
you're quite the schemer.

33:15.310 --> 33:17.330
That's called frugality.

33:17.880 --> 33:19.530
My father taught me that.

33:19.960 --> 33:20.860
Silver-tongued, aren't you?

33:21.070 --> 33:22.980
It's called being articulate. I got that from my mother.

33:25.640 --> 33:26.380
Wu Zhiqi?

33:31.310 --> 33:31.770
Get inside.

34:26.360 --> 34:27.900
Darling, how do you plan to repay me?

34:28.400 --> 34:29.690
We've been husband and wife for over 20 years,

34:30.000 --> 34:30.650
and you're still making demands?

34:31.030 --> 34:33.090
Even between husband and wife, accounts should be kept clear.

34:34.390 --> 34:35.310
Let's hear it, then.

34:36.670 --> 34:37.650
How about this?

34:38.190 --> 34:39.690
Grant me one request after we're out of here.

34:40.840 --> 34:41.210
All right.

34:41.590 --> 34:42.530
No hesitation?

34:42.960 --> 34:44.530
Aren't you worried I might ask you to rob, kill,

34:44.840 --> 34:45.650
or set fires?

34:47.070 --> 34:47.690
Would you?

34:48.590 --> 34:49.340
No.

34:50.150 --> 34:50.900
But

34:52.230 --> 34:54.700
I might make my husband sell his body.

34:54.840 --> 34:56.210
Cut the flirting in front of me.

34:56.840 --> 34:57.980
Hand over the Star Stone now!

34:58.760 --> 35:00.300
So that's what you came to steal.

35:01.360 --> 35:02.860
I heard the high-rank Green Ape demon Wu Zhiqi

35:02.880 --> 35:03.740
committed a grave crime

35:03.960 --> 35:05.900
and got imprisoned by the Dragon Deity in the Blackwater River.

35:06.590 --> 35:07.940
Even chains that thick

35:07.960 --> 35:08.690
couldn't hold you?

35:09.320 --> 35:10.300
If you know better,

35:11.590 --> 35:12.490
hand over the Star Stone now,

35:13.510 --> 35:14.210
or else...

35:14.230 --> 35:15.300
What do you want the Star Stone for?

35:16.360 --> 35:17.420
That's none of your concern.

36:41.280 --> 36:42.860
Boy,

36:44.110 --> 36:45.570
talk about a hasty retreat.

37:07.630 --> 37:08.130
Master...

37:10.440 --> 37:11.210
Master?

37:18.360 --> 37:20.090
Why did you call me that, sir?

37:21.760 --> 37:22.780
Master,

37:24.070 --> 37:24.740
do you know each other?

37:26.280 --> 37:27.210
We've never met.

37:29.590 --> 37:31.090
Besides, I've long returned to secular life.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.690
I'm no master anymore.

37:34.000 --> 37:35.170
But I know who you are.

37:38.710 --> 37:39.780
You're

37:41.000 --> 37:42.170
from the Western Regions. You're that...

37:42.710 --> 37:43.460
That demon monk?

37:48.280 --> 37:49.010
That's right.

37:50.070 --> 37:51.900
I'm the demon monk who betrayed the Buddha

37:52.840 --> 37:54.090
and fell into the evil path.

37:55.800 --> 37:57.260
People call me

37:59.920 --> 38:00.780
Xie Lingxi.

38:05.760 --> 38:07.090
Why do you know me?

38:11.440 --> 38:12.130
I just

38:13.920 --> 38:15.780
recognized the Twelve Thoughts in your hand.

38:18.400 --> 38:20.130
How do you know the Twelve Thoughts?

38:27.510 --> 38:29.980
Thank you, Master, for saving us just now.

38:30.440 --> 38:31.300
Wu Zhiqi, the Green Ape,

38:31.320 --> 38:32.260
will probably come back again.

38:32.670 --> 38:33.820
Please stay

38:34.150 --> 38:35.210
and lend us a hand.

38:40.000 --> 38:40.490
I...

38:41.840 --> 38:43.260
I didn't mean to offend you.

38:45.630 --> 38:46.570
I can stay,

38:50.400 --> 38:51.740
on one condition.

38:53.110 --> 38:54.780
Every meal must come with mushrooms,

38:56.920 --> 38:57.380
right?

39:02.190 --> 39:02.780
No problem.

39:16.140 --> 39:17.300
♪It's your light♪

39:17.500 --> 39:19.380
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

39:19.540 --> 39:22.660
♪That set the night alight♪

39:23.020 --> 39:29.540
♪And lead me through the fight♪

39:31.300 --> 39:33.180
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

39:33.620 --> 39:38.060
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

39:38.860 --> 39:40.540
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

39:40.700 --> 39:46.100
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

39:46.860 --> 39:52.260
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

39:54.580 --> 40:00.620
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

40:01.580 --> 40:03.740
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

40:04.020 --> 40:08.860
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

40:09.220 --> 40:11.540
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

40:11.740 --> 40:16.820
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

40:17.060 --> 40:19.060
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

40:19.340 --> 40:23.700
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

40:24.700 --> 40:31.660
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

40:48.220 --> 40:51.180
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

40:52.260 --> 40:55.660
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

40:56.460 --> 40:58.980
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

40:59.220 --> 41:02.300
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

41:02.700 --> 41:05.020
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

41:05.540 --> 41:09.940
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

41:10.180 --> 41:12.340
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

41:12.740 --> 41:17.700
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

41:17.940 --> 41:19.100
♪It's your light♪

41:19.300 --> 41:21.140
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

41:21.340 --> 41:24.460
♪That set the night alight♪

41:25.220 --> 41:34.660
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
